
                   <p style="text-align: center">
                       <b>Title:</b> Restoring the default template
The following table shows the format of the default email template.<br>
                       <b>Bounding box:</b> x1=185, y1=323, x2=1516, y2=798
                   </p>
                   <div align="center"><table border="1" class="dataframe">
  <thead>
    <tr style="text-align: right;">
      <th></th>
      <th>0</th>
      <th>1</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <th>0</th>
      <td>Field</td>
      <td>Default value</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>1</th>
      <td>From</td>
      <td>log@$location</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>2</th>
      <td>Subject</td>
      <td>[$severity] $shortText</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>3</th>
      <td>Body</td>
      <td>The following event occurred on $date: $fullText\nReason:\n$reason\nAction:\n$action\nDetails:\nUser: $user\nOrigin: $origin</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table></div>
